card.title: Phonics, Letters & Sounds: Phase 1 - Make That Word

metadata.author: Yoto
metadata.description: This card introduces your child to blending and segmenting - breaking words down into the sounds they are made up of and putting them back together again. This is the final step before entering the more formal aspects of learning to read.
